text: always always amazing food. enjoy it every single time without fail it's amazing. a good place for takeaway or a quick snack. love their rice combo. staff are so friendly and gives a good portion of extra sauce when requested. limited seating tho. dining in at this outlet not recommended for more than 4 Pax.

The skewer of chicken & pork isn’t tender. The meat ball taste mashy and isn’t at all savoury. The small amount of sauce drizzle over the rice is unable to moisten the texture of the rice. However still a long queue of patrons. It used to be good but not now…
Food and service is fine. However if you eat in, further inside got a long table. When you look up it is full of dusts! Sigh

Twice a week i came here. I loves this food so much, especially with extra sauce.. Yummy.
Staffs very very friendly. Highly recommended.
Delicious. Sit down,  eat in with rice and seaweed  garnish, plus their delicious sauce, is a real delight.
